{"tid":109620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC圖輯：不丹小王子周歲生日","createTime":"2017-02-06T05:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T18:21:54.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbae23bc69309cafef2b0d1593fe890e9162274d","tid":109620,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2017/02/04/20170204-044616_U3250_M244248_b768.jpg?itok 8ya_Zv5G\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F20170204-044616_U3250_M244248_b768.jpg%3Fitok%208ya_Zv5G&h=88a791f8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一名粉絲在臉書上發文說，「所有的娃娃都很可愛，但是不丹小王子讓我心情特別激動。」（BBC中文網）<br />\n<br />\n不丹小王子吉格梅將滿1歲，王室發佈小王子超萌最新照片，慶祝小王子生日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2017/02/04/20170204-044616_U3250_M244244_88c7.jpg?itok m73K6dUW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F20170204-044616_U3250_M244244_88c7.jpg%3Fitok%20m73K6dUW&h=f199e178&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n位於喜馬拉雅山的不丹號稱「全世界最幸福國家」，2月5日是不丹國王楚旺克和王后佩瑪誕下的小王子吉格梅一歲生日。王室發佈吉格梅的超萌最新照片，慶祝小王子生日。（BBC中文網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2017/02/04/20170204-044616_U3250_M244250_396e.jpg?itok 7VVhbYKd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F20170204-044616_U3250_M244250_396e.jpg%3Fitok%207VVhbYKd&h=4cd9af15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在佛教中，樹木象徵著長壽、健康和慈悲。在佛教國家不丹，數以萬計的民眾種植1萬多棵樹來慶祝國王吉格梅&middot;凱薩爾&middot;納姆耶爾&middot;旺楚克與王后耶特松&middot;佩瑪喜得王子。（BBC中文網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2017/02/04/20170204-044616_U3250_M244247_801f.jpg?itok r0kgdBOs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F20170204-044616_U3250_M244247_801f.jpg%3Fitok%20r0kgdBOs&h=d581a72a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n這其實不是小王子吉格梅第一次當日曆「模特兒」。去年9月的月曆中，小王子身穿不丹傳統服飾，三張照片展示不同的表情，十分逗趣。（BBC中文網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2017/02/04/20170204-044616_U3250_M244249_b6df.jpg?itok me8EqNRa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F20170204-044616_U3250_M244249_b6df.jpg%3Fitok%20me8EqNRa&h=695c79dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佛教國家不丹有80萬人口，而國王旺楚克和王后佩瑪深受人民愛戴。國王和王后是在結婚5年後，於2016年2月5日迎來小王子。（BBC中文網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2017/02/04/20170204-044616_U3250_M244245_e8b9.jpg?itok -PZpaXRu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F20170204-044616_U3250_M244245_e8b9.jpg%3Fitok%20-PZpaXRu&h=be164cc0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不丹1999年才有了互聯網，王室利用社交媒體不斷改變自己的形像。 王后經常在臉書上發表她個人的王室照片。（BBC中文網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800xauto-er/s3/media/image/2017/02/04/20170204-044616_U3250_M244246_36aa.jpg?itok OxWJHW49\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800xauto-er%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F20170204-044616_U3250_M244246_36aa.jpg%3Fitok%20OxWJHW49&h=96ffc6aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不丹王宮發言人對BBC表示，不丹民眾都想保護小王子，並成為小王子生活的一部分。她說：「我們都為看到他的成長，並成為他成長過程中所有里程碑的一部分而感到自豪。」（BBC中文網）"},{"pid":"05d0542a6686849974fa473bfa4f4718ed6588fb","tid":109620,"uid":68916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:52:57.000Z","msg":"王后幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3ddcef9e9e2cf19187db6e62c3bee99991f857","tid":109620,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e50e007777501e76f5658e948ed18250da1655c","tid":109620,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52cc67041d5a571b36689645b9776cc3fbe6b9a","tid":109620,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T10:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebc3c7e0a975babaecbfb8a39b899dcbe074fc9","tid":109620,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:34:12.000Z","msg":"種樹黎慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d26c171ff4ccb69cd287c2f7e65f8da284ba8f","tid":109620,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"以老豆老母基因嚟講都算唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465be5e7c6aad8f13f00f02c57b8deee85871b70","tid":109620,"uid":10976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614a36b7847f1c621bdec0b411cfcfe56e97ac65","tid":109620,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:53:24.000Z","msg":"小國寡民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16d83f68dcf5d396170057bea994f60483cbdf4","tid":109620,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:48:44.000Z","msg":"佢老豆基因太強&hellip;&hellip;定老母整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6777f71ea66c6912e8270895f06e7eb5463e28","tid":109620,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小國寡民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n印度隻狗"}]}